author: KATE FELDMAN
title: Gisele Bündchen celebrates Tom Brady, Patriots' Super Bowl win
text:
Gisele Bündchen can’t contain her excitement as husband Tom Brady and Patriots win Super Bowl LI Gisele Bündchen celebrates Tom Brady, Patriots' Super Bowl win NEW YORK DAILY NEWS  53 AM 
While Tom Brady celebrated his fifth Super Bowl win, Gisele Bündchen cheered on her husband from the stands. 
The Brazilian supermodel went crazy as the Patriots pulled off a comeback against the Falcons to win Super Bowl LI 34-28. 
The 36-year-old was spotted jumping for joy after the final overtime touchdown before her phone goes flying out of her hand during one particularly rambunctious leap. Gisele Bündchen celebrates with 4-year-old daughter Vivian after husband Tom Brady and the Patriots pull off an improbable Super Bowl comeback. (Kevin C. Cox/Getty Images) 
Bündchen was tweeting and posting photos throughout the stressful game, but there’s still no word of what she was filming when her phone slipped from her fingers — or whether the device survived the fall.
